Description: # simple cli demo project
        
        
        ## how to running
        
        * init venv
        
        ```code
        python3 -m venv .
        ```
        
        * install click pacakge
        
        * activate venv
        
        ```code
        source bin/activate
        ```
        
        * install click pacakge
        
        ```code
        pip install click
        ```
        
        * install with pip pacakge for test
        
        ```code
        pip install .
        ```
        
        * test cli
        
        ```code
        dalongcli --name dalong --count 3
        ```
        
        result
        
        ```code
        Hello, dalong!
        Hello, dalong!
        Hello, dalong!
        ```
